snippet.title: Culture & Camaraderie EP33 Purpose Fuels Perfomance | ft. Jussie Smolett, Amber Heard & Drake x URL
snippet.description:
Hello Comrades, 
This is the coming of the newest instalment of the Culture and Camaraderie podcast with  myself ARAH of @NYTypical & Tyler @Lax_Era.. On this weeks most thought provoking introspective industrious creative discussion:

 we talk a lot about character performance and purpose. who people really are and how they act, Including Jussie Smollet, Johnny Depp Amber Heard and Drake URL TV Smack Caffeine App merger, Justin Briber producer using Splice in cultural conversation... 

We broach some deep topics in the midst of all that We talk about ourselves being a man and what it takes to live up to the expectations of being a man and the worth and value of our work. Bringing up names like Slowthai and Royce Da 5'9
